gomodel:SYNGO_1368  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: The figure shows the synaptic co-localization of 4E-BP1 with synapse in hippocampal neurons (P2; 14 DIV), furthermore 4E-EBP1 colocalize with PSD-95, postsynaptic marker.\n\n24/9/2017 Pim\n- Literal: \"The mTOR-positive regions were observed in the dendritic shaft in a diffuse pattern that extended into synaptic regions (Fig. (Fig.33Al). Consistent with the notion of postsynaptic localization of these proteins, double labeling with PSD-95 showed the signals from eIF-4E, 4E-BP1, and mTOR at synaptic regions almost completely overlapped with PSD-95 signals.\". Experimental description: Sprague-Dawley" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2094-7491" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4419-210X" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1190-4481" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9848-0262" ;
        dc:date           "2017-11-13" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_1368" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10116" .

